# Development

To spin up the docker stack (frontend accessible on port 3000):
```bash
docker compose up
```

## Frontend
Start the development server on `http://localhost:3000`:
```bash
pnpm run --dir=frontend dev
```

Build the application for production:

```bash
pnpm run --dir=frontend build
```

Locally preview production build:
```bash
pnpm run --dir=frontend preview
```

## Backend
Start the GraphQL server:
```bash
uv --directory=backend run uvicorn backend_api.entrypoint:app --reload --host '::' --port 4000
```

## Updating from the template
This repository uses a copier template. To pull in the latest updates from the template, use the command:
`copier update --trust --conflict rej --defaults`{% endraw %}
